                        <h3 class="sub_category_title">Fivetran @ Runway.com</h3>
                        <ul class="sub_category_content">
                           <li>Designed, built and led a team of 3 on Runway's Integrations effort, based on Fivetran,
                              Merge.dev,
                              Workato, and other direct connections to data (Rippling.com, Puzzle.io, ...).</li>
                           <li>Sources consumed into Snowflake and Postgres, and served/transformed to/by end users via
                              APIs and React UI.</li>
                           <li>Heavy use of Fivetran's Transformations, Connect Cards, Go SDK, REST API,
                              and Webhooks. </li>
                           <li>Backed by bespoke Go binary, Snowflake, and Postgres.</li>
