                     </section>
                     <section class="sub_category">
                        <h3 class="sub_category_title">The Runway Data Model</h3>
                        <ul class="sub_category_content">
                           <ul class="sub_category_content">
                              <li>Architected and led a team of 5 in implementing a PostgreSQL-backed, versioned
                                 datastore, with custom ORM, custom constraint triggers, and optimized throughput.</li>
                              <li>Live, incremental migration from previously bespoke datastore, to newly designed
                                 system: O(100M) rows.</li>
                              <li>Made the argument for redesigning Runway's data model/store, and convinced leadership
                                 it was worth doing.
                              <li>Wrote the canonical documentation distributed to the rest of the engineering team,
